        }
    });

    function getCookie(name) {
        var nameEQ = name + "=";
        var cookies = document.cookie.split(';');
        for (var i = 0; i &lt; cookies.length; i++) {
            var c = cookies[i];

            while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
                c = c.substring(1, c.length);
            }
            if (c.indexOf(nameEQ) == 0) {
                return c.substring(nameEQ.length, c.length);
            }
        }
        return null;
    }

    $(function () {
        function changeCurrency(currency) {
            if (window.onCurrencyUpdate) {
                
                window.onCurrencyUpdate(currency);
                return;
            }
            if (Viator.isCheckoutEvent) {
                $('input[name="currencyCode"]').val(currency);
                $('#checkoutForm')
                        .attr('action', '/booking/checkoutChangeCurrency.jspa')
                        .submit();

                return;
            }

            $.ajax({
                url: "/changeCurrency.jspa?currencyCode=" + currency,
                success: function (data) {
                    if (data.status !== 'success') {
                        location.href = '/error.jspa';
                        return false;
                    }

                    
                    
                    if (Viator.$errorBox.is(":visible")
                            &amp;&amp; Viator.$quoteForm != undefined) {
                        Viator.$quoteForm.removeAttr("id");
                        $("body").append(Viator.$quoteForm);
                        Viator.$quoteForm[0].submit();
                    } else if (location.href.indexOf('applyPromoCode.jspa') &gt; -1 ||
                                    location.href.indexOf('error.jspa') &gt; -1) {
                        location.href = '/shopping-cart';
                    } else {
                        if (location.hash) {
                            location.replace(location.href.replace(location.hash, ''));
                        } else {
                            location.replace(location.href);
                        }
                    }
                    
                },
                error: function () {
                    location.reload();
                }
            });
        }

        Viator.$errorBox = $(".error-box");

        if (location.href.indexOf("sicPriceQuote") !== -1
                &amp;&amp; Viator.$errorBox.is(":visible")) {
            Viator.$quoteForm = $("#quoteform").clone();
        }

        

        var $currencies = $('a[data-currency]');

        $currencies.click(function (e) {
            e.preventDefault();

            if ($(this).data('currency') !==  $currencies.eq(0).data('currency')) {
                changeCurrency($(this).data('currency'));
            }
        });
    });

class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Guergana was an excellent guide, who was very knowledgable and made the tour fun for our family, including 3 grandchildren visiting from the West Coast. Would recommend highly to anyone visiting DC who wants an overview and has 2 hours to take this tour. One can exit on the Mall at one of the Smithsonian exhibits, to keep exploring as you desire.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(35762596);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="34669768" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Daniel S" /> <a title="Daniel S" href="/profile/34444814" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Daniel S" href="/profile/34444814"> Daniel S</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> July 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Julia was very knowledgable and exuded personality and wit making the tour so much more interesting. Mike was great and answered all of my questions. I would recommend it to everyone.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(34476159);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="34444072" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Gage B" /> <a title="Gage B" href="/profile/34224430" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Gage B" href="/profile/34224430"> Gage B</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> July 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>I highly recommend this tour! We learned so much from our tour guide Sasha about all the history and myths of the city!!! She was an absolute pleasure!!!</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(34444072);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="34385119" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Alan S" /> <a title="Alan S" href="/profile/19000805" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Alan S" href="/profile/19000805"> Alan S</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> July 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Great way to visit main sites in Washington DC in a small group with a guide. Travelling around in electric cart was easy and allowed for quick hop on hop off at various sites. Rachel, our guide was great fun and very informative, she really made the trip for us. Our 2 teenage daughters also really enjoyed it and the fact that it was just two hours was perfect. Would definitely recommend.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(34385119);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="34311637" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Catherine M" /> <a title="Catherine M" href="/profile/34211131" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Catherine M" href="/profile/34211131"> Catherine M</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> July 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Monte was a fantastic tour guide. The electric cart tour was the perfect way to begin our exploration of DC and helped us prioritize what we wanted to see in the few days we had in DC. We felt lucky to get such a fun and knowledgeable tour guide - Monte did such a fantastic job and exceeded our expectations.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man pricing</span><i class="via-caret-right"></i></p> </div> </a> <a href="#quoteform" class="top-link inverse-txt"><i class="via-arrow-north img mtm"></i>Top</a> </div> </div> <div id="34217478" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Justin D" /> <a title="Justin D" href="/profile/32979309" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Justin D" href="/profile/32979309"> Justin D</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> July 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Our tour guide, Stephen, was AWESOME! He made our trip fun and educational. This tour is a great way to see the highlights of the city and then decide where you want to spend more time. We did get to spend time at the Capital, then one or other (though we were able to squeeze in both by being quick!) Lincoln or Vietnam War Memorial, and the MLK memorial. The rest were drive-by's, but Stephen was great at stopping at places for great photo ops. </p> <p>Pros: <br /> -Stephen! So informative! I think a tour guide can make or break your trip and he was fabulous. <br /> -No other way could you get in this much sight seeing in such a short amount of time. <br /> -Small tour group - car can fit 7 riders max.<br /> -'Open air' car - got a good breeze throughout the ride that kept us cool in 90 degree heat.<br /> -Tour guide has flexibility with where to drop you off (so you could hit one of the Smithsonian's for example and have 'free' drop off right there!<br /> -Great for families with older children - because of so much to see and not stopping much, the kids stayed interested the whole time.</p> <p>Cons: <br /> -If you want to stop and spend time at all monuments, you don't get to do this on the tour. I thought the description on their website can make it sound like you don't stop anywhere, but you do get a few in.<br /> -Not sure how younger kids would do on this tour. But then, why are you taking young kids to D.C.? You might just rethink your vacation spot!</p> <p>Recommendation: Book this tour EARLY in your trip so you can make better choices on where to spend the rest of your time. You could spend WEEKS in D.C. and not see it all!</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(34217478);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="32426023" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Tim H" /> <a title="Tim H" href="/profile/32038464" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Tim H" href="/profile/32038464"> Tim H</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> May 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>I don't know where to start.... i highly recommend this tour for someone limited on time or with slight disability someone that cant walk great distance, however there is some walking .Our tour guide was the greastest, she really knew her facts and the history of washington. We really saw a lot in the 2 hour tour, more than i ever thought we would. I WAS REALLY INPRESSED !!!</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(32426023);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="31736100" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Bruce N" /> <a title="Bruce N" href="/profile/31398545" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Bruce N" href="/profile/31398545"> Bruce N</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> April 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>This was a great way to start our week in DC. Mike our tour guide and driver was exceptional. He knew the history, sights and inside stories about not only the historical sites around the National Mall but also the buildings and culture of the city. He made us feel right at home. Two thumbs up for Mike. I would highly recommend this tour and ask for Mike. Thanks again.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(31736100);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="31689062" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="lcoffey47" /> <a title="lcoffey47" href="/profile/9039473" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="lcoffey47" href="/profile/9039473"> lcoffey47</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> April 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Sophia was an amazing tour guide. Being brought up in the DC area she had lots of insider historical information. It was like a private tour as there were only 4 of us. We were able to get up close to many of the sites for pictures. With the Electric Cart you can see things you wouldn't on a tour bus. We had time to walk down the Vietnam wall and also climb up in the Lincoln Memorial. A very enjoyable 2 hours.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(31689062);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="31688733" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="robtuck" /> <a title="robtuck" href="/profile/31573351" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="robtuck" href="/profile/31573351"> robtuck</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> April 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>Great way to see the a number of sights in a short period of time. It feels more like a walking tour since you are not enclosed in a bus. Our tour guide, Stephen, was great and had immense knowledge of the popular sights in Washington, D.C. He mixed interesting facts with funny anecdotes and provided his own local recollections.</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(31688733);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="31667540" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Mark M" /> <a title="Mark M" href="/profile/30889385" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="Mark M" href="/profile/30889385"> Mark M</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> April 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>This tour was one of the highlights of our trip. Our tour guide Guergana was very knowledgeable and a lot of fun too! She even had our boys 12 and 16 hanging on every word. We recommend highly!!</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall" onclick="return Viator.Common.reportProblemWindow(31667540);">Report problem</a> </p> </div> </div> <div id="31586864" class="lighter-border-t pvmm" itemprop="review" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Review"> <div class="media man"> <div class="img"> <div itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <meta itemprop="name" content="harr4" /> <a title="harr4" href="/profile/8734468" itemprop="url"> <img alt="" src="/wayfinder/images/avatar_default_45x45.png" class="img-circle" width="45px" height="45px" itemprop="image" /> </a> </div> </div> <div class="bd"> <p class="large note mvn"> <a title="harr4" href="/profile/8734468"> harr4</a> <span class="xsmall note"> </span> </p> <div class="mbm" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Rating"> <meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="bestRating" content="5" /> <meta itemprop="worstRating" content="1" /> <div class="unit mrs mlm" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended"> <img alt="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" title="5 star rating: Highly Recommended" src="/images/stars/orange/16_5.gif" /> </div> <span class="xsmall note"> April 2018 </span> </div> <div class="cms-content mhm" itemprop="reviewBody"> <p> </p><p>This is definitely the way to start your DC trip. Our driver/guide, Chris, was excellent! He knows everything there is to know about the monuments/museums and was spot on with his must see advice and tips on seeing them. He also gave us a great list of area restaurants that covered every cuisine you might be interested in! Highly recommend this tour, and if your lucky enough to get Chris, all the better!</p> <p></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="line no-print"> <p class="man unitRight"> <a href="" class="xsmall"
